{"tid":630294,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哥迪奧拿：我寧願去打GOLF都唔想睇曼聯d波","createTime":"2018-04-15T13:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T17:44:33.000Z","uid":119778,"like":47,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d8a6e94c33dc317ccc1f9be503cc273f306f7e49","tid":630294,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T13:19:55.000Z","msg":"曼聯今晚若不敵西布朗，曼城就可以提早封王，不過曼城領隊哥迪奧拿表示不會看球賽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-performgroup-com.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w680/s/images.performgroup.com/di/library/GOAL/22/be/pep-guardiola-manchester-city_12vmzolsb76or1ra3kldatpd0j.jpg?t=-944565854&amp;quality=100&amp;w=640&amp;h=360 \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-performgroup-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw680%2Fs%2Fimages.performgroup.com%2Fdi%2Flibrary%2FGOAL%2F22%2Fbe%2Fpep-guardiola-manchester-city_12vmzolsb76or1ra3kldatpd0j.jpg%3Ft%3D-944565854%26quality%3D100%26w%3D640%26h%3D360%20&h=630ab666&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n哥迪奧拿最快今晚就可以贏得自己首個英超冠軍，但他表示要去打哥爾夫球，沒有空看曼聯對西布朗的球賽。<br />\n<br />\n「我有3天假，我會打哥爾夫球、陪囝囝及陪朋友。」<br />\n<br />\n對於對熱刺一戰，哥迪奧拿表示要對今季其中一名最佳領隊普捷天奴的球隊絕不容易，但當比賽進行10至15分鐘後，就知道今季冠軍會到手，不是今天，不是明天也不要緊，冠軍一定會到手。<br />\n<br />\n「球員們的表現很出色，上一周的成績的確對他們很不公平。」<br />\n<br />\n「下一場我們會對史雲斯，我們將會努力在那場賽事成為冠軍。」"},{"pid":"83979ced01d2c7324ac5ee0791cddeea52a3935a","tid":630294,"uid":4578,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T13:21:01.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d185ff56e2cf6b2d4765cf781cd998fc9e259f","tid":630294,"uid":137238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T13:21:03.000Z","msg":"又click bait<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f80a2149857c79d9c85af8a8b3dfe7548873c83","tid":630294,"uid":8636,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T13:42:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又click bait<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hk